snippet.title: Alien Breed™: Impact  - Out Now for PC from Steam and for PlayStation®3 from PSN.
snippet.description:
BUY NOW and download the PC demo now from http://bit.ly/ABSteam  

Also available for PlayStation®3 through digital delivery on PlayStation® Network: http://bit.ly/PS3AB1 

Alien Breed: Impact is an explosive science fiction arcade-shooter that resurrects a much revered franchise with an epic story, swarms of highly intelligent alien enemies, high-impact weapons, highly detailed and rich environments; all implemented with superb technology in a state-of-the-art gaming experience. In addition to the thrilling single-player campaign mode, the game offers a relentless, action-packed, online two-player co-operative battle mode.

Team17, founded in 1990, are a fully independent video game developer and publisher responsible for the Worms™ series, Alien Breed and Superfrog. Ensure you never miss out on our latest videos by subscribing to us now: http://bit.ly/SubscribeT17.

Don't forget you can also
Like us on Facebook: http://bit.ly/LikeAlienBreed
Follow us on Twitter: http://bit.ly/FollowT17
